How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Learn more how customers reviews work on Amazon

5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent Tablet
Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
Color: SilverSize: 32GBVerified Purchase
Let me start off by saying that I have had several K***** tablets (I'm sure you know which ones I'm referring to. I'm hoping that by not naming them that this review won't be taken down.) Those tablets didn't come close to the quality and usability of this one. First of all it's much faster. It doesn't bog-down the way the K*****s do. I can get decent apps from the Google Playstore rather than the proprietary junk I had to use on the other devices. The setting feature is very well organized. A really nice feature is that since I have a Galaxy phone, I've been able to link the tablet to it. If I'm using my tablet and receive a text, I don't have to put it down and pick up my phone. I just view, and respond to, the text on my tablet. My pictures and other docs are synced. The camera is pretty good but the one on my phone is a bit better. My only complaints are that it's a bit slow to start (roughly a minute rather than the 30 seconds I was used to.) The other thing is that the frame seems to be narrower than I'm used to. I'm always turning pages when I don't intend to. But that might just be my way of holding it. The battery life could be a bit longer. But other than those few minor things, I can find no fault with it. I highly recommend this tablet; especially if you have a Galaxy phone.

5.0 out of 5 stars EXCELLENT tablet for general use!
Reviewed in the United States on April 4, 2024
Color: Dark GraySize: 32GBVerified Purchase
My husband bought me this tablet for Christmas, and I ended up liking it so much that I bought him one too! Let me start by saying I use this for general activities (Netflix, check email, playing games, upload/store photos, etc). It has worked wonderfully for me. It is a sleek thin design, functions well and quickly, doesn't have issues loading videos or using Netflix, and it's a good price compared to other tablets on the market. I see some negative reviews related to it's function, but I personally have not had any issues... maybe I am not expecting too much from a tiny tablet or maybe I don't overuse mine, but it has worked as well as any other tablet for me. Screen quality is great in my opinion, although I have also seen some reviewers complain (again, maybe I just have lower expectations. who knows?).

Overall, if you have realistic expectations of tablets, this is an excellent purchase and I highly recommend. If you are looking for a tablet to work as flawlessly as a $1,000 PC, maybe lower your expectations or perhaps buy a PC.

Anyway, I hope you found this review helpful!

Reviewed in the United States on April 1, 2024
Color: Dark GraySize: 32GBVerified Purchase
In the realm of tablets, finding the perfect blend of versatility, entertainment, and functionality can be a challenge. However, the SAMSUNG Galaxy Tab A8 10.5” Android Tablet effortlessly rises to the occasion, offering a comprehensive solution for users of all ages and interests. After spending considerable time exploring its features, I'm excited to share my insights into what makes this tablet a standout choice in its category.

Let's start with the centerpiece of any tablet—the display. The Galaxy Tab A8 boasts a spacious 10.5-inch LCD screen that delivers a visual feast of vibrant colors and sharp details. Whether you're watching movies, playing games, or browsing the web, the immersive display elevates your viewing experience to new heights. With its generous size, the screen provides ample room for productivity tasks, making it equally suited for work and play.

One of the standout features of the Galaxy Tab A8 is its focus on family-friendly entertainment. Equipped with a wealth of pre-loaded kids' content, including educational games, videos, and books, the tablet becomes a gateway to endless hours of fun and learning for children. Parents can rest easy knowing that their kids are exploring a safe and enriching digital environment, thanks to the dedicated Kids Home mode and robust parental controls.

Beyond its entertainment capabilities, the Galaxy Tab A8 shines as a versatile productivity tool. With Smart Switch integration, transferring files, apps, and settings from your old device is a seamless process, ensuring a smooth transition to your new tablet. Whether you're managing emails, editing documents, or organizing your schedule, the tablet's intuitive interface and responsive performance keep you productive and connected on the go.

Under the hood, the Galaxy Tab A8 packs a punch with its octa-core processor and 3GB of RAM, delivering snappy performance that effortlessly handles multitasking and demanding applications. With 32GB of internal storage and support for expandable storage via microSD card, you'll have plenty of space to store your favorite apps, photos, and videos without compromise.

Design-wise, the Galaxy Tab A8 exudes elegance and sophistication with its slim profile and premium metallic finish. The lightweight and portable form factor make it easy to take with you wherever you go, whether you're commuting to work or relaxing at home. Plus, with up to 13 hours of battery life on a single charge, you can enjoy uninterrupted entertainment and productivity throughout the day.

In conclusion, the SAMSUNG Galaxy Tab A8 10.5” Android Tablet sets a new standard for versatility and entertainment in the tablet market. Whether you're a busy professional, a tech-savvy parent, or a casual user looking for a reliable companion, this tablet delivers a premium experience that caters to your every need. With its stunning display, family-friendly features, seamless performance, and sleek design, the Galaxy Tab A8 is a true powerhouse that exceeds expectations. Highly recommended for anyone seeking a top-tier Android tablet experience.
